00:18:54.970 --> 00:18:58.380 align:middle line:10%
And so now we're walking around
and we know we don't feel safe.

00:18:58.380 --> 00:19:00.437 align:middle line:10%
And we need Mother
Earth connected to us

00:19:00.437 --> 00:19:02.520 align:middle line:10%
up through our feet and
up through our base chakra

00:19:02.520 --> 00:19:06.940 align:middle line:10%
to feel like we're going
to stay on the planet.

00:19:06.940 --> 00:19:10.740 align:middle line:10%
So that's a base chakra
typical trauma is an accident.

